Package: libqtglassflow0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qt/OpenGL liquid glass effect rendering library
 A lightweight library providing real-time liquid glass visual effects
 with SDF-based superellipse shapes and smooth-union sticky bridging.

